# Save Schema Context

You are touching persisted runtime-state schemas or save DTO contracts. Read these docs before adding/removing persisted fields:

1. `docs/design/core-architecture.md` — shared contracts and terminology
2. `docs/design/save-contract-quick-reference.md` — ownership rules + size budget policy
3. `docs/design/save-and-progression.md` — canonical payload expectations and exact-restore guarantees

Load only the domain docs that correspond to the modules you are editing.

Avoid loading generic `*State*` / `*Instance*` files unless they are directly involved in persisted save contracts for the task.

When adding/changing persisted fields, update the payload contract, save/load module, and save tests together.
